---
const contactSectionUrl = "#contato";
---

<section
  class="ateb-grid-pattern relative overflow-hidden pb-16 pt-[clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem)] md:pb-24"
  id="hero"
>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_12%_22%,rgba(179,209,51,0.18),transparent_24%),radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_30%,rgba(179,209,51,0.14),transparent_22%),radial-gradient(circle_at_86%_72%,rgba(77,72,55,0.08),transparent_20%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="ateb-container relative">
    <div
      class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:min-h-[calc(100vh-10rem)] lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:gap-14"
    >
      <div class="grid gap-6 text-center lg:text-left">
        <h1
          class="font-sora mx-auto max-w-[18ch] text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-[1.06] tracking-[-0.06em] text-ateb-dark lg:mx-0"
        >
          Consultoria em ERP para transformar processos em performance
        </h1>

        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[680px] gap-4 lg:mx-0">
          <p
            class="text-[clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.16rem)] leading-[1.7] text-[rgba(77,72,55,0.84)]"
          >
            Sua empresa usa TOTVS RM, Protheus, Fluig ou Sankhya, mas ainda
            enfrenta retrabalho, controles manuais ou processos pouco
            integrados?
          </p>

          <p
            class="text-[clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.16rem)] leading-[1.7] text-[rgba(77,72,55,0.84)]"
          >
            A ATEB Solucoes apoia empresas na consultoria, automacao e
            integracao de sistemas ERP, com mais de 20 anos de experiencia para
            gerar mais controle, produtividade e organizacao.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex w-full flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 pt-2 lg:justify-start"
        >
          <a
            href={contactSectionUrl}
            class="inline-flex min-h-[3.35rem] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ateb-lime px-7 py-3.5 text-center text-sm font-extrabold text-ateb-dark shadow-[0_18px_35px_rgba(179,209,51,0.25)] transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_24px_45px_rgba(179,209,51,0.34)] sm:w-auto"
          >
            Solicitar diagnostico estrategico
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[rgba(77,72,55,0.72)]">
          Atendimento para empresas em todo o Brasil.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[560px] lg:mx-0 lg:ml-auto">
        <div
          class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-[12%] bottom-[6%] h-10 rounded-full bg-[rgba(29,18,10,0.16)] blur-[26px]"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="pointer-events-none absolute right-[8%] top-[8%] h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-ateb-lime/20 blur-3xl"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>

        <img
          src="/images/hero.webp"
          alt="Imagem institucional da ATEB Solucoes"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          class="relative mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-[520px] object-contain drop-shadow-[0_30px_50px_rgba(29,18,10,0.16)]"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
